{"tid":2186841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Youtuber不甘寂寞，深夜迫肌肉男高中生鑽小樹林！日本網友：瘋了吧…","createTime":"2020-09-03T08:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T08:34:07.000Z","uid":109923,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ea212d6d92b8e794f60c838b84ddf8f94a8575a0","tid":2186841,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:48:36.000Z","msg":"　　白皙纖細的他深夜潛入高中足球部男生宿舍，把熟睡中的健壯少年，帶到公園企圖強姦&hellip;這種要素過多的情節，你也許會覺得只是小說或本子裡虛構的&hellip;但，它真的發生在現實當中了！就在最近，日本千葉縣的一樁真實案件裡，這個名叫 森岡優十的女裝Youtuber就做出了以上種種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mTQwTaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmTQwTaZ.jpg&h=e86c1b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n他看上去雖然溫和無害，甚至有點小帥，但其實本性讓人難以置信。<br />\n<br />\n　　7月25日淩晨3點左右，他因為「無法抑制」，拿著利器潛入了自己住處附近的一所高中足球部男生宿舍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSK5XC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSK5XC2.jpg&h=1dca6b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 　　為什麼潛入得這麼容易呢？不是他天賦異稟，是校方為了防止疫情，讓學生宿舍在開著冷氣的情況下，房間依然能不密封，保證空氣流通，就讓學生們開著窗戶睡覺。再加上足球部白天訓練辛苦，部員們都睡得很沉，同寢室的人都沒察覺到有人進來了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rL86G4O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrL86G4O.jpg&h=54747783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（男生宿舍）<br />\n<br />\n　　受害學生也是足球部的一員，一個被曬得黝黑身材健壯的高中生，白天訓練累得不行，淩晨正是睡得沉的時候，卻被潛進來的森岡優十拿著利器叫醒。也許是怕說話聲音和動作驚醒其他人，森岡一邊嚇他，一邊把他轉移到另一個空房間。並且逼迫他做XX行為，高中生拒絕後森岡還不死心，打算把他帶到附近的公園裡進行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZxHWjRJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZxHWjRJ.jpg&h=05a320f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　之後高中男生找到機會逃跑，日媒是這樣描述當時的狀況的，「深夜的公園裡，有兩名年輕男子，被曬得黝黑的肌肉少年逮到空子逃了，白皙的纖細男子體力跟不上，追不上他。」看著足球少年越跑越遠的背影，未遂的森岡也逃了。高中男生回去就報了警，孩子真的好慘，在宿舍睡著覺都能碰上這種無妄之災，不幸中的萬幸就是沒有受傷，不過直面這種場景，肯定留下心理陰影了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnNSCDy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnNSCDy.jpg&h=7c9eeab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　警方接到報案之後，立馬開始了搜查，並且很快鎖定了森岡，但在最初的這次逮捕調查中，森岡否認了自己的嫌疑。不過有周邊的監控錄影等決定性證據，他終究是難逃懲罰。"},{"pid":"53466608cba1d47cd8c72070ab1b2fbc1693a31a","tid":2186841,"uid":58254,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c772421f7514b1ebd92d7440cec16cf9cc2e1fb0","tid":2186841,"uid":178078,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過戴返頂假髮應該呃到好多男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166b9bb0340842a793f13701936da1d685e22fc7","tid":2186841,"uid":109923,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c772421f7514b1ebd92d7440cec16cf9cc2e1fb0","tid":2186841,"uid":178078,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過戴返頂假髮應該呃到好多男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/none/41c00c41eec947333068e505b9d0826d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200903/_2020090313282173342.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F41c00c41eec947333068e505b9d0826d%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200903%2F_2020090313282173342.jpg&h=7c6d9b67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d0a10bd9a14a3036b31e604a32190afab528cae","tid":2186841,"uid":27319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:56:25.000Z","msg":"gv情節<img src